caption: An energetic hip-hop banger with hard-hitting 808 bass, crisp hi-hats, and aggressive male rap vocals. The production features trap-style percussion, dark synth stabs, and a hypnotic melody that builds intensity throughout the track.
lyrics:
[Intro]
Yeah, let's go
You already know what it is

[Verse 1]
Started from the bottom now I'm climbing to the top
Haters tried to stop me but I never gonna stop
Grinding every day yeah I'm putting in the work
Diamonds on my wrist and I'm flexing on the earth
Came up from nothing had to hustle for the bread
Now I'm living large got these visions in my head
They said I couldn't make it but I proved them all wrong
Now I'm writing history putting pain into this song

[Chorus]
Rise up, rise up, we don't fall
Stand tall, stand tall, through it all
Rise up, rise up, hear the call
We the ones who run it all

[Verse 2]
Every scar I got is just a story that I tell
Went through heaven and I walked right out of hell
My ambition is a fire that will never burn out
This is what success and dedication's all about
Late nights early mornings yeah I paid the price
Rolled the dice and now I'm living paradise
To my day ones yeah I got you till the end
This ain't just a moment this a legacy my friend

[Chorus]
Rise up, rise up, we don't fall
Stand tall, stand tall, through it all
Rise up, rise up, hear the call
We the ones who run it all

[Outro]
Yeah, we made it
This just the beginning
